OL,5, A vicar who sexually abused a          
OL,6, three-year-old has been jailed for the 
OL,7, "extremely wicked series of acts".     
OL,9,FGordon Newton, 40, who worked in       
OL,10,FBatley, West Yorkshire, abused the girl
OL,11,Fon a number of occasions.              
OL,13,FLeeds Crown Court heard he had         
OL,14,Fconfessed to having a sexual interest  
OL,15,Fin children for a number of years.     
OL,17,FA judge branded Newton a "hypocrite"   
OL,18,Fand said he had committed "a gross     
OL,19,Fabuse of trust" as he sentenced him to 
OL,20,Fnine years and seven months.           
